text: Outstrider is the second studio album by Norwegian black metal band Abbath. It was released on 5 July 2019 through Season of Mist. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== ===Abbath=== * Abbath Doom Occulta – vocals, guitars, songwriting, arrangements (tracks 1, 5, 7, 8) * Ukri Suvilehto - drums * Mia Wallace - bass * Ole André Farstad - guitars (lead, acoustic, baritone), zither, songwriting (guitar leads), arrangements (tracks 1, 5, 7, 8) ==Charts== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders" |- !
